        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "See https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/27223#issuecomment-4061732540\n\n\n> Is there an api to change the current tab to another tab?\n\nI assume your question was [answered](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/27223#issuecomment-2726012932): `nvim_get_current_win`. Note also that `nvim_win_set_config` can move a (non-float) window to another tabpage since 0.10. Also works for float windows since Nvim 0.12 https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/35816.\n\n\n",
